      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "新增四类约束：\n  • API 规范\n    （RESTful + request_id 追踪）\n  • 认证（JWT 15min + 7d refresh）\n  • CORS（允许 GitHub Pages 域名）\n  • 测试（Jest+RTL / pytest）",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
