      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#331166",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "没有阶段门禁\n规格可随时修改\n\n迭代 而非 瀑布\n简单 而非 复杂\nBrownfield-first\n\n适合存量系统改造\n嵌入 AI 编码工作流",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "没有阶段门禁\n规格可随时修改\n\n迭代 而非 瀑布\n简单 而非 复杂\nBrownfield-first\n\n适合存量系统改造\n嵌入 AI 编码工作流",
